rther education. But positive crew atmosphere may offset communication difficulty? Egocentric could be problematic for teamwork. However, other candidates have more severe teamwork deficits. Candidate B is unreliable in teamwork. Candidate A lacks teamwork. Candidate D lacks teamwork. So Candidate C appears best overall.\n\nThus vote for Candidate C.\n\nNow produce public message: summarize all known attributes, weigh strengths/weaknesses, note missing info (e.g., no explicit teamwork for A and D, but we have positive crew atmosphere for C). Conclude with vote."}
